{"word":"G2869 - κοπάζω - kopázō - kop-ad'-zo - Cease","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοπάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kopázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kop-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அமர், நின்றுபோ"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to grow weary or tired; to cease from violence, to cease raging"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2873 - κόπος - kópos - kop'-os/2873\">G2873</a>; to <i>tire</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>relax:</i> - cease."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}